flow.mentorSays:
Let's understand what this Show/Hide Toggle challenge asks for.

**Challenge Description:**
// Create a component that:
// - Has a button labeled "Show Details"
// - When clicked, displays a paragraph of text
// - Button text changes to "Hide Details"
// - Clicking again hides the text
// - Text toggles on each click

**What we need to build:**
This challenge tests your understanding of Conditional rendering, state.

**Time estimate:** 5 minutes
**Difficulty level:** Junior

This is a practical interview question that tests your understanding of core Angular concepts and your ability to implement them correctly.

